flowchart TD
    A[Stack + Input] --> B{Can reduce?}
    B -->|Yes| C{Should shift instead?}
    B -->|No| D{Input remaining?}
    C -->|No| E[Reduce]
    C -->|Yes| F[Shift-Reduce Conflict]
    D -->|Yes| G[Shift]
    D -->|No| H{Stack = Start symbol?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Accept]
    H -->|No| J[Error]
    E --> A
    G --> A
